<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10603610>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–7. Types of Nesticella mollicula and N. inthanoni. 1, Lectotype of Nesticella mollicula, habitus, dorsal view. 2, ditto, ventral view. 3, ditto, epigyne, ventral view. 4, ditto, original label. 5, epigyne of N. inthanoni (after Lehtinen & Saaristo 1980). 6, holotype of N. inthanoni, habitus, dorsal view. 7, ditto, epigyne, ventral view.Abbreviations: Co, copulatory opening; S, spermatheca; Sc, scapus. Photos: 1–4 A. Tanasevitch; 6, 7: K. Kaunisto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10603610/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

